{"tid":1134493,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"猁狗係咁屌牙蘇鏟草 好嬲嬲豬","createTime":"2019-05-01T20:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T20:40:57.000Z","uid":201601,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8ef27fb4ab0e0e494ac93a42931b28c6dcb7f5","tid":1134493,"uid":201601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T20:04:38.000Z","msg":"錢又唔係畀得多人<br />\n<br />\n冠軍又畀唔到人<br />\n當年咁撚carry都畀謝四條撚樣玩走咗個英超<br />\n<br />\n當年英國啲妓者係咁屌9牙蘇嗰陣<br />\n猁物浦又做啲咩幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢依家喺巴塞又有幾何畀啲妓者帶頭屌<br />\n<br />\n依家猁場上嗰啲人對佢嚟講全部又三唔識七咁制（除咗神軒）<br />\n<br />\n牙蘇鏟草又有咩問題，當人哋當年喺到踢咗幾年波就大撚曬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f74dcff8f360e140863791622155dcbe41bfd8d","tid":1134493,"uid":74334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T20:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V36pZ5e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV36pZ5e.gif&h=0ebbc88e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d34bbdb2e8c298e61ddf6671491e6060eeefa2e","tid":1134493,"uid":201601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7f74dcff8f360e140863791622155dcbe41bfd8d","tid":1134493,"uid":74334,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T20:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V36pZ5e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV36pZ5e.gif&h=0ebbc88e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T20:12:40.000Z","msg":"啲隊友咁閪都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686b084f6106e070a699e8836ec486d8374344cf","tid":1134493,"uid":